OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,FNigel told ITV News' Charlotte Gay the
OL,7,Fclub had helped people reconnect with
OL,8,Fold friends.
OL,10,FA breakfast club for "grumpy" old men
OL,11,Fin Cornwall to help them cope with
OL,12,Fbereavement, illness and loneliness
OL,13,Fhas seen a massive leap in membership.
OL,14,FThe (Mostly) Grumpy Old Men's
OL,15,FBreakfast Club started with three
OL,16,Fpeople and now has over 180 regular
OL,17,Ffaces coming to their monthly meet-ups
OL,18,Fin Redruth.
