OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,FIt was founded by Nigel Jeffery in
OL,7,F2021 after his wife died Bev died from
OL,8,Fcancer. He says its quite
OL,9,F"overwhelming" how popular its become.
OL,11,F"A couple of friends said lets go for
OL,12,Fbreakfast just to spend some time, to
OL,13,Fhelp me in my grief to start with."
OL,14,F"Anybody who knows me know I like to
OL,15,Ftake photographs to put on Facebook
OL,16,Fand lots of people saw it and wanted
OL,17,Fto join."
