OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,FThe rapid increase in numbers meant
OL,7,Fthe group has to move from a diner in
OL,8,Ftown to a much bigger venue at the
OL,9,FPenventon Park Hotel.
OL,11,FNigel says with so many coming along
OL,12,Ffor the Friday breakfasts lots of
OL,13,Fpeople have reconnected with old
OL,14,Ffriends and met those they have a lot
OL,15,Fin common with.
