OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,F"They come here and talk. On the last
OL,7,Fbreakfast there was eight people sat
OL,8,Faround the table and they all that
OL,9,Fprostate cancer and all talked about
OL,10,Fthat. Cos you think you're on your own
OL,11,Fbut you're really not."
OL,13,FThe grumpiness is a bit tongue in
OL,14,Fcheek and while mediator Stephen
OL,15,FWetherelt jokes he's there to keep the
OL,16,Fgrumpiness on track he says there is a
OL,17,Fbig "social need" for this group.
