OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,FAnother regular member, David Horman
OL,7,Fsays while it's nice to have a chat,
OL,8,Fit's the impact on people's "mental
OL,9,Fhealth".
OL,11,F"There are friends here that have lost
OL,12,Fpartners, some of us have been
OL,13,Faffected by illnesses. It's just nice
OL,14,Fto chat openly because men don't."
