OL,3,C'Grumpy' breakfast club helps men feel
OL,4,Cless isolated in illness and grief
OL,6,FThe popularity of this mens group has
OL,7,Fled to Nigel offering a helping hand
OL,8,Fto launch a women's spin off - Ladies
OL,9,Fwho Brunch - and now he jokes he needs
OL,10,Fto franchise the grumpy club across
OL,11,Fthe duchy.J"A lady from Bude North
OL,12,FCornwall, phoned me and said her
OL,13,Fbrother lost his wife six months ago
OL,14,Fand wondered if we had anything out
OL,15,Fthere. So yeah I may go to North
OL,16,FCornwall."JThe breakfast club also
OL,17,Ffundraises hundreds of pounds each
OL,18,Ftime they meet-up for a local charity
OL,19,Fand in March they supported the Terry
OL,20,FPryor Trust.
